{"tid":1468722,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"建議割蓆撚可以好好向狗隊學習團結精神","createTime":"2019-08-13T20:17:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T06:39:29.000Z","uid":36543,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"80df441056a2faec90c0088593c4c1c0a7c4740f","tid":1468722,"uid":36543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T20:17:36.000Z","msg":"轉載，唔知有冇人post 左未<br />\n<br />\n不割蓆，一齊向警隊學習團結精神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n問：阻塞機場搞死香港？<br />\n答：「做法不完美，但可接受，要改善。」<br />\n<br />\n問：點解阻止公安離開？<br />\n答：「佢唔喺現場出現就冇事，去得果度就可能有呢啲風險」<br />\n<br />\n問：阻止救護帶佢離開？人命黎架。<br />\n答：「而家眾說紛云，我認為事主可以去報警先，警方必定會跟進調查。」<br />\n<br />\n問：點解你地咁方人性，濫用暴力，究竟想點？答：「在場嘅市民只係用最低武力，當一切平靜後，真誠對話就會展開」"},{"pid":"6d9012bac3de0f607ae57f9042cfef63ecb0745c","tid":1468722,"uid":36543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T20:19:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a4d391539099d20f88947157e356b3906c5df01","tid":1468722,"uid":36543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:49:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a997cc8f0927bb7e3aa79ef732a94601064943e0","tid":1468722,"uid":36543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:30:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24b09217ac07193bff2d9219bb6b32cb6b806613","tid":1468722,"uid":36543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:30:24.000Z","msg":"你屌我駁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c701a8109969f4b001edbb58cfc5048a1783989","tid":1468722,"uid":265305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"80df441056a2faec90c0088593c4c1c0a7c4740f","tid":1468722,"uid":36543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T20:17:36.000Z","msg":"轉載，唔知有冇人post 左未<br />\n<br />\n不割蓆，一齊向警隊學習團結精神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n問：阻塞機場搞死香港？<br />\n答：「做法不完美，但可接受，要改善。」<br />\n<br />\n問：點解阻止公安離開？<br />\n答：「佢唔喺現場出現就冇事，去得果度就可能有呢啲風險」<br />\n<br />\n問：阻止救護帶佢離開？人命黎架。<br />\n答：「而家眾說紛云，我認為事主可以去報警先，警方必定會跟進調查。」<br />\n<br />\n問：點解你地咁方人性，濫用暴力，究竟想點？答：「在場嘅市民只係用最低武力，當一切平靜後，真誠對話就會展開」"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:33:28.000Z","msg":"屌，好清晰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UQFM4nS.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUQFM4nS.gif&h=a74ab43d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UQFM4nS.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUQFM4nS.gif&h=a74ab43d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UQFM4nS.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUQFM4nS.gif&h=a74ab43d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔知道指責前線既人咩諗法定係一毛，解釋一次：<br />\n係政府（共黨)<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>A行為</strong></span>只會煲大對自己有利既point ， <br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">B行為</span></strong>冷處理所有已fc做錯既事（狗濫權），<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">C行為</span></strong>無中生有屈對方 (收錢遊行)<br />\n對方係政權(港共+狗)，香港人係冇權冇槍既市民。<br />\n孫中山人數上由壓倒毛澤東到落敗到台灣，係衰左係政治上唔夠老毛賤格，做唔出BC行為。 <br />\n示威者人數由200萬到而加有大量因爲爆玻璃行為搖擺不定而減到唔知得返幾多。<br />\n要贏到共黨政權得一樣方法 <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">A</span><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">B</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">C</span>行為</strong>做得誇過對方。<br />\n盲撐可能用錯字，我用攬字。<br />\n攬等於= <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">A</span> +<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">B</span></strong><br />\n你話道徳淪喪既？ 我明白。但請唔好係打仗時期對外大宣稱自己友做錯呀喪屌呀。想屌咪整連儂牆囉。 <br />\n連登都幾多淺黃中立入黎睇，唔好做衰示威者團結形象啦。<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><ins>欣賞冇被狗搞到憤怒蒙蔽自己既大家</ins></span>，亦希望大家明白政權歷史到現在既手段一樣污穢不堪，我地冇殺人冇姦淫冇大屠殺，<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">用返抹黑老作還擊對方時，你可以做唔出，但請放下政治潔癖，冷處理自己友做得唔好既地方，擁護自己友直至打低強權。</span></strong></span><br />\n最後，五毛三毛一毛死三代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b467701c0037374f5a62c2d5b886b228a4829b8d","tid":1468722,"uid":36543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:34:30.000Z","msg":"以上呢四句基本上係無敵，大家拎去用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13c0808c02246971bcb72c5085f53d6c12d307da","tid":1468722,"uid":36543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:36:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5400c5e8128fa9004e98a96610ec1f12e26f1b50","tid":1468722,"uid":297230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:39:29.000Z","msg":"<strong>屎橋一條：大家其實有無考慮過準備定塊布隨時掛係身寫住</strong><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">平反六四</span></span></strong>？<br />\n如果咁樣<br />\n大陸應該唔夠膽出街同要係微博block &amp;狂剷好多大陸人嘅post<br />\n等大陸人直接感受下言論自由係咩黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nPush"}]}